Fayraska RNA wuxuu ka soo baxa cytoplasm; ka dib markii uu fayraska kala qaybsamo, fayraska RNA wuxuu ku soo galaa daboolka glycoprotein iyo borotiinka nucleocapsid wuxuu sameeyaa vesicle oo leh virion, kaas oo ku biira plasma si uu u soo saaro fayraska.
