Calaamadaha cudurka: Sawirada laabta iyo kororka calaamadaha cudurka ee hooseeya waa in lagu tixgeliyaa iyadoo la tixgelinayo arrimo kale si loo ogaado badbaadada COVID-19 iyo dhibaatooyinka soo raaca.
