Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ka jira gudaha (xabaalaha unugyada) sanbabada, muruqyada, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay xakameysaa isbeddelka angiotensin-to-enzyme (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa heerarka angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadida ang ((1-7) taas oo ka dhigaysa daawo aad u awood badan oo lagu daaweeyo cudurka wadnaha. ACE2 sidoo kale waxaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu xakameeyo coronavirus.
Enzyme-ka aadanaha waxaa lagu magacaabaa hACE2.
Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 waa metalloprotein oo ku jira zinc ee dusha sare ee unugyada iyo unugyada kale.
Badeecada ACE2 waxaa ku jira N-terminal peptidase M2 iyo C-terminal receptor ee sanka ee loo yaqaan 'amino acid receptor'.
ACE2 waxay ka kooban tahay nooc ka mid ah borotiinka xarkaha ah ee xarkaha ah, iyada oo ay ku shaqeyneyso inay noqoto enzyme-ka ka baxsan unugyada iyo unugyada kale.
Meelaha ka baxsan unugyada ee ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaraa transmembrane-ka oo leh enzyme kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, ka dibna borotiinka ayaa loo sii daayaa dhiigga ka dibna waxaa lagu sii daayaa dheecaan.
ACE2 waxaa lagu dhex dhejiyaa xubno badan: ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay xuubka unugyada sanbabada nooca II ee unugyada alveolarenterocytes ee mindhicirka yar, xididdada iyo xididdada endothelial iyo muruqyada fudud ee unugyada unugyada ee xubnaha.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale lagu helaa gudaha maskaxda, striatum, hypothalamus, iyo maskaxda.
Waxqabadka ugu weyn ee aCE2 waa in la sameeyo waxqabadka ACE.
ACE waxay ku xirtaa hormoonka angiotensin I iyo angiotensin II.
ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay amino acid-ka carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine ee angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-pPhe) waxayna ku dhejisaa angiotensin (1-7) ee vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale ku xidhan tahay peptides badan sida [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale hagaajineysaa xannibaadda xuubka ee amino acid-ka dhexdhexaadka ah ee SLC6A19 ee ka soo horjeeda cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 waa xarunta ugu horreysa ee unugyada coronavirus, iyo sidoo kale HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus-ka SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka COVID-19).
Si loo fahmo, isku xirnaanta SARS-CoV S1 ee SARS-CoV2 ee borotiinka ACE2 ee unugyada sare waxay horseedi doontaa endocytosis waxayna ku wareejineysaa fayraska unugyada mid ka mid ah endosomes-ka unugyada.
